    "If the similarity score exceeded this threshold, the matched content from the knowledge base was considered valid.",
    "Otherwise, a warning message stating \"No valid information retrieved for this question\" was output.",
    "During the question-answering procedure, when a user input a question, the BGE model retrieved semantically relevant information from a local knowledge base.",
    "The top five retrieved pieces of information were then sent to GPT-4 and combined with the users' questions to generate a response.",
    "The program automatically recorded both the questions and final answers."
